<BOS_TOKEN><|START_OF_TURN_TOKEN|><|USER_TOKEN|>You are playing a collaborative word guessing game in which you have to describe a target word for another player to guess.

Rules:
(a) You have to reply in the form: CLUE: <some text>. Guesses from the other player will start with GUESS.

(ii) If the other player can guess the target word in 3 tries, you both win.

- result
